text: The Dutch Wikipedia () is the Dutch-language edition of Wikipedia. This edition was started in June 2001. It became the 3rd largest edition in April 2013, but has since dropped to sixth.Wikimedia list of Wikipedias and their statistics.. Retrieved January 4, 2021.
